{"tid":562816,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Paul Thomas Anderson新片 Phantom Thread討論區","createTime":"2018-02-16T09:06:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T22:57:06.000Z","uid":5063,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"96cf444169051143bc821b9f65182da718a962f1","tid":562816,"uid":5063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T09:06:24.000Z","msg":"六項奧斯卡提名，包括best Picture, best director<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDaniel day-lewis息影作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>故事簡介</strong><br />\n<br />\n50年代的倫敦，才華橫溢的服裝設計師雷諾士（丹尼爾戴路易斯 飾）和姊姊西妮（李絲莉曼維爾 飾）經營時裝品牌，為皇室、明星及名流貴族設計別樹一格的高級訂製服。雷諾士的生命有許多女人來來去去，給予獨身主義的他源源不絕的創作靈感&hellip;&hellip;直到年輕倔強的艾瑪（維琪嘉莉絲 飾）成為他真正的靈感女神。高傲的才子漸漸因這關係而陷入混亂，以往一板一眼、精心編織的生活開始偏離軌道。他無法接受眼前的失控狀態，卻難以抵抗愛情的誘惑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=xNsiQMeSvMk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxNsiQMeSvMk&d=6R1NWmwuYKdQhY7l7wlf8fjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=c055a225\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=xNsiQMeSvMk</a><br />\n<br />\n三月八號香港上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742974dc28a7d3aa544d36d6f54961ef2a9c3abd","tid":562816,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T09:11:56.000Z","msg":"其實香港有冇機會上到菲林版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e9d6fb167d0d89fa9a4469acfe161d28d770f6","tid":562816,"uid":5063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T09:13:09.000Z","msg":"個故事寫得好好，講一種好特別既愛情觀，Daniel day-lewis同個女主角d演技冇得輸，題材唔係PTA拍開既類型，但係主角interaction d 位拿捏得好好，個結局好正，建議大家去睇支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949d9c5311094388268abab9739fbd93ba0387fd","tid":56